<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11461</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>16656</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那天晚饭后，妈妈在洗碗，乔伊在擦碗。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16657</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23276</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的发表主题是‘建立友谊’，我已经读了书里我的部分，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23277</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28524</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>还在网上查了相关资料。” 乔伊跟家人们说道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28525</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31529</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“凯蒂的主题是‘运动’。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31530</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34895</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂在看她的《健康管理》书。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34896</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37642</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我还没读我那部分呢！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37643</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42199</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不过，我已经知道为什么运动对我们有好处了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42200</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45505</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在我只需要像贝柔老师说的那样，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45506</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51054</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>发挥我的想象力，写出一份有意思的发表就行了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51055</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55716</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你可以让全班同学一起运动。” 乔伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55717</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59459</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这个主意很好。” 爸爸说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59460</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62185</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么运动？” 凯蒂问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62186</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68945</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“开合跳？”乔伊突然转身跳离了洗碗槽，开始做开合跳。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68946</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71847</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈拿走了乔伊手里的杯子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71848</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74772</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“小心！别把杯子打碎了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74773</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79123</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这个不符合我的发表主题。” 凯蒂说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79124</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81662</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“爷爷，您觉得呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81663</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89235</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“在我看来，在花园里干活或是收拾房间就是一种运动。” 爷爷说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89236</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94368</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果孩子们能做家务的话，也会很健康的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94369</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98492</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别开玩笑了，爷爷。” 凯蒂说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98493</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100791</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是认真的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100792</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104302</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“爸爸，你觉得呢？” 凯蒂说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104303</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108121</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们可以跑步。” 爸爸提议说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108122</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111765</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“跳舞怎么样？” 乔伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111766</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115188</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“波尔卡舞！” 爷爷说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115189</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120120</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他拉着乔伊，在厨房里跳起舞来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120121</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124501</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好晕啊，爷爷！” 乔伊笑着说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127695</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“方块舞怎么样？” 爸爸说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127696</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131187</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“ 让你的舞伴转起来！”他喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131188</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136513</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爸爸挽起乔伊的胳膊，和她转圈跳起舞来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136514</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141273</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“图书馆里好像有一些方块舞的音乐。” 妈妈说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141274</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145167</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这个好像很有意思！” 凯蒂说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145168</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147319</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她想了一会儿，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147320</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151424</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我得教全班跳舞。乔伊，你愿意帮忙吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151425</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153199</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当然！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153200</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156832</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“明天，我要问问卡洛斯和卢克！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156833</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂小声嘟哝着，用手拍了一下额头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161503</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166233</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哎呀！我差点儿忘了！我还在生卢克的气呢！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166234</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169998</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你得先原谅他。” 乔伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169999</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175092</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天早上，乔伊看见了卢克和卡洛斯。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175093</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179143</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他们又在和奥利维亚说话。” 凯蒂嘟哝着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179144</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182237</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>奥利维亚转身走向双胞胎。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182238</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185453</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我给你们带了礼物。” 奥利维亚说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185454</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188986</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是我从夏威夷带回来的 ‘ALOHA’ 铅笔。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188987</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194796</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>奥利维亚递给凯蒂和乔伊一人一支浅粉色的铅笔。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194797</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197185</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢！” 乔伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197186</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200584</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢！” 凯蒂也说道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205227</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你猜‘ALOHA’ 是什么意思？” 卡洛斯说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205228</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209524</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是‘你好’ 的意思，对吧？” 乔伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209525</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214726</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对。”奥利维亚说，“不过，也有‘再见’ 的意思！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214727</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218576</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好奇怪啊！” 凯蒂忍不住说道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218577</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223185</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卢克看着她。“你还在生我的气吗？” 他问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223186</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225689</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没有。” 凯蒂说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225690</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229045</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对了，我要发表的主题与运动有关，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229046</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231754</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>想请你帮忙，你有兴趣吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231755</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234508</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好啊！” 卢克说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234509</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238444</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果你在找擅长运动的男生，你就找对人了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238445</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241877</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你呢，卡洛斯？” 凯蒂说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241878</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243936</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯，我会帮你的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243937</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247627</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卡洛斯弯曲胳膊，摸了摸自己的肌肉，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247628</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251188</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们可以做一些俯卧撑。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251189</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256141</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不，我不打算做俯卧撑 。” 凯蒂说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256142</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258556</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我需要你们跳方块舞。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258557</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“方块舞？” 卢克和卡洛斯喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>262503</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265713</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“绝对不可能！” 卡洛斯说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265714</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269117</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不跳方块舞！” 卢克说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269118</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270869</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我什么舞也不跳！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270870</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>276025</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对不起，太晚了，没法取消了。” 凯蒂说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>276026</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278037</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们已经同意了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278038</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>283893</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可是，我们连方块舞怎么跳都不知道。卢克，是吧？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>283894</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287104</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那不是问题。” 凯蒂说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>287108</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>290011</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们打算星期六在我家练习。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>290012</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>293020</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一定会很有趣的！” 奥利维亚说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>293021</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>295372</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂眨了眨眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>295373</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>300352</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“奥利维亚以为我也让她来了吗？” 凯蒂想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>76</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>300353</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>305455</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“呃......我只需要四个人。” 她马上说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>77</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>305456</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>310809</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“两个男生，两个女生。卢克、卡洛斯，乔伊和我。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>78</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>310810</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>313202</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们会教同学们舞步。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>79</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>313203</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>317569</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦。” 奥利维亚说着低下了头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>80</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>317570</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>320077</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊也低下了头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>81</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>320078</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>324543</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她想邀请奥利维亚，但她知道自己不可以，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>82</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>324544</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>327381</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>因为那是凯蒂的发表。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>83</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>327382</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>330472</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那我们都说好了。” 她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>84</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>330473</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>333036</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂回头看着其他人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>85</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>333037</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>335599</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别忘了！是星期六下午一点。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>86</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>335600</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>340864</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>别忘了戴牛仔帽！哈！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>